Sione: We've just brewed a pot of tea, would you like some?

Izumi: So, you there~ I see you're a diligent and careful one, eh?
Izumi: Let me give you a reward~ The Spring Waters Hotel is all yours!
Newcomer: What?
Newcomer: —Ehh!!!?
Beyata: Yao... Are you leaving without saying goodbye?
Beyata: The contraband's been destroyed. If only we could all be here to thank you properly... I'm sure everyone would be overjoyed~
Beyata: Yao... Were you familiar with Miss Blossom and Miss Orchid?
Beyata: They freed themselves and didn't have to work on Hot Spring Street anymore. But they're still legendary idols in the eyes of the girls who remain~
Beyata: But, at the same time, they've been making our lives difficult... What was it all for? They must know the trouble they've been causing to Izumi and the rest of us...
Yao: ...They were simply doing whatever they could to keep themselves afloat.
Yao: And they just didn't care how many people they trampled over to achieve it.
